# Testing Phases Index

> Modular, phase-based testing framework.
> Each phase builds on previous phases.

---

## Overview

Testing is organized into sequential phases. Each phase:
- Has explicit prerequisites (previous phases)
- Tests a specific feature area
- Has clear success criteria
- Documents common issues

