## Quick Reference

### Running a Single Phase

```bash
# Run phase 2 tests
npm test -- --grep "Phase 2"
# or
pytest -k "phase_2"
```

### Running All Phases

```bash
npm run test:phases
# or
pytest tests/phases/
```

